    "import zipfile\n",
    "import os\n",
    "\n",

    "zip_path = 'C:/Users/86173/Desktop/archive.zip'\n",
    "\n",
    "# 解压目标文件夹\n",
    "extract_to = 'archive_extracted'\n",
    "os.makedirs(extract_to, exist_ok=True)\n",
    "\n",
    "# 解压压缩包\n",
    "with zipfile.ZipFile(zip_path, 'r') as zip_ref:\n",
    "    zip_ref.extractall(extract_to)\n",
    "\n",
    "print(\"✅ 解压完成！文件已保存至：\", extract_to)\n"
   ]

    "    clean_str = str(installs_str).replace(',', '').replace('+', '')\n",
    "    try:\n",
    "        return float(clean_str)\n",
    "    except:\n",
    "        return np.nan\n",
    "\n",
    "def clean_price(price):\n",
    "    \"\"\"清洗价格数据\"\"\"\n",
    "    if pd.isna(price):\n",
    "        return 0.0\n",
    "    if isinstance(price, str):\n",
    "        # 移除货币符号\n",
    "        price = price.replace('$', '').replace('€', '').replace('£', '')\n",
    "        try:\n",
    "            return float(price)\n",
    "        except:\n",
    "            return 0.0\n",
    "    return float(price)\n",
    "\n",
    "# 数据清洗\n",
    "print(\"\\n=== 数据清洗 ===\")\n",
    "df['Rating'] = pd.to_numeric(df['Rating'], errors='coerce')\n",
    "df['Rating_Count'] = pd.to_numeric(df['Rating Count'], errors='coerce')\n",
    "df['Price_Clean'] = df['Price'].apply(clean_price)\n",
    "df['Installs_Clean'] = df['Minimum Installs'].apply(clean_installs)\n",
    "\n",
    "\n",
    "# 移除缺失值和异常值\n",
    "df_clean = df.dropna(subset=['Rating', 'Price_Clean', 'Installs_Clean'])\n",
    "# 移除评分为0的应用（通常表示没有评分）\n",
    "df_clean = df_clean[df_clean['Rating'] > 0]\n",
    "# 移除安装量为0的应用\n",
    "df_clean = df_clean[df_clean['Installs_Clean'] > 0]\n",
    "\n",
    "print(f\"清洗后数据集形状: {df_clean.shape}\")\n",
    "\n",
    "# 对于大数据集，我们可以进行采样以提高分析效率\n",
    "if len(df_clean) > 100000:\n",
    "    print(\"数据集较大，进行分层采样...\")\n",
    "    # 按类别进行分层采样\n",
    "    sample_size = min(50000, len(df_clean))\n",
    "    df_sample = df_clean.groupby('Category', group_keys=False).apply(\n",
    "        lambda x: x.sample(min(len(x), max(1, int(sample_size * len(x) / len(df_clean)))), \n",
    "                          random_state=42)\n",
    "    ).reset_index(drop=True)\n",
    "    print(f\"采样后数据集形状: {df_sample.shape}\")\n",
    "    # 使用采样数据进行后续分析\n",
    "    df_analysis = df_sample.copy()\n",
    "else:\n",
    "    df_analysis = df_clean.copy()"
   ]

    "def nonlinear_modeling(df):\n",
    "    \"\"\"\n",
    "    4. Non-linear modeling: Explore complex relationship patterns with Downloads as dependent variable\n",
    "    \"\"\"\n",
    "    print(\"\\n=== 4. Non-linear Modeling Analysis (Downloads as Target) ===\")\n",
    "    \n",
    "    df_model = df.copy()\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # 准备建模数据 - 下载量作为因变量\n",
    "    # 对下载量进行对数变换以处理偏态分布\n",
    "    df_model['Log_Installs'] = np.log10(df_model['Installs_Clean'] + 1)\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # 自变量：评分和价格\n",
    "    X = df_model[['Rating', 'Price_Clean']].fillna(0)\n",
    "    # 因变量：下载量（对数变换）\n",
    "    y = df_model['Log_Installs'].fillna(df_model['Log_Installs'].mean())\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # 填充评分缺失值\n",
    "    X['Rating'] = X['Rating'].fillna(X['Rating'].mean())\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # 移除异常值以提高模型稳定性\n",
    "    mask = (np.abs(stats.zscore(X)) < 3).all(axis=1) & (np.abs(stats.zscore(y)) < 3)\n",
    "    X_clean = X[mask]\n",
    "    y_clean = y[mask]\n",
    "    \n",
    "    print(f\"建模数据大小: {len(X_clean)}\")\n",
    "    print(f\"因变量: Log(下载量), 自变量: 评分, 价格\")\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # 4.1 多项式回归（不同阶数）\n",
    "    degrees = [1, 2, 3, 4]\n",
    "    models = {}\n",
    "    scores = {}\n",
    "    \n",
    "    for degree in degrees:\n",
    "        # 创建多项式特征\n",
    "        poly_model = Pipeline([\n",
    "            ('poly', PolynomialFeatures(degree=degree, include_bias=False)),\n",
    "            ('scaler', StandardScaler()),\n",
    "            ('regressor', LinearRegression())\n",
    "        ])\n",
    "        \n",
    "        # 训练模型\n",
    "        poly_model.fit(X_clean, y_clean)\n",
    "        y_pred = poly_model.predict(X_clean)\n",
    "        score = r2_score(y_clean, y_pred)\n",
    "        \n",
    "        models[f'poly_{degree}'] = poly_model\n",
    "        scores[f'poly_{degree}'] = score\n",
    "        \n",
    "        print(f\"多项式回归 (阶数 {degree}): R² = {score:.4f}\")\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # 4.2 评分的分段回归分析\n",
    "    from scipy.optimize import minimize\n",
    "    \n",
    "    def piecewise_linear(x, a, b, c, d, breakpoint):\n",
    "        \"\"\"分段线性函数\"\"\"\n",
    "        return np.where(x <= breakpoint, a * x + b, c * x + d)\n",
    "    \n",
    "    def piecewise_loss(params, x, y):\n",
    "        \"\"\"分段回归损失函数\"\"\"\n",
    "        a, b, c, d, breakpoint = params\n",
    "        y_pred = piecewise_linear(x, a, b, c, d, breakpoint)\n",
    "        return np.sum((y - y_pred) ** 2)\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # 仅对评分进行分段回归\n",
    "    x_rating = X_clean['Rating'].values\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # 初始参数估计\n",
    "    initial_params = [1.0, 0.0, 0.5, 2.0, np.median(x_rating)]\n",
    "    \n",
    "    try:\n",
    "        result = minimize(piecewise_loss, initial_params, args=(x_rating, y_clean),\n",
    "                         method='Nelder-Mead', options={'maxiter': 1000})\n",
    "        \n",
    "        if result.success:\n",
    "            a, b, c, d, breakpoint = result.x\n",
    "            y_pred_piecewise = piecewise_linear(x_rating, a, b, c, d, breakpoint)\n",
    "            piecewise_score = r2_score(y_clean, y_pred_piecewise)\n",
    "            \n",
    "            print(f\"分段线性回归 (基于评分): R² = {piecewise_score:.4f}\")\n",
    "            print(f\"  转折点位置: 评分 = {breakpoint:.2f}\")\n",
    "            print(f\"  左段斜率: {a:.4f}, 右段斜率: {c:.4f}\")\n",
    "        else:\n",
    "            print(\"分段回归优化失败\")\n",
    "            piecewise_score = 0\n",
    "            breakpoint = 0\n",
    "    except:\n",
    "        print(\"分段回归计算错误\")\n",
    "        piecewise_score = 0\n",
    "        breakpoint = 0\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # 4.3 可视化建模结果\n",
    "    fig, axes = plt.subplots(3, 2, figsize=(16, 18))\n",
    "    fig.suptitle('非线性建模结果 (下载量作为因变量)', fontsize=16, fontweight='bold')\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # 创建预测网格\n",
    "    rating_range = np.linspace(X_clean['Rating'].min(), X_clean['Rating'].max(), 100)\n",
    "    price_median = X_clean['Price_Clean'].median()\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # 4.3.1 不同阶数多项式回归比较\n",
    "    for i, degree in enumerate(degrees):\n",
    "        if i < 4:  # 只显示前4个\n",
    "            X_pred = np.column_stack([rating_range, np.full_like(rating_range, price_median)])\n",
    "            y_pred = models[f'poly_{degree}'].predict(X_pred)\n",
    "            \n",
    "            row, col = i // 2, i % 2\n",
    "            axes[row, col].scatter(X_clean['Rating'], y_clean, alpha=0.3, s=10)\n",
    "            axes[row, col].plot(rating_range, y_pred, 'r-', linewidth=2, \n",
    "                              label=f'多项式 (阶数 {degree})')\n",
    "            axes[row, col].set_xlabel('评分')\n",
    "            axes[row, col].set_ylabel('Log(下载量)')\n",
    "            axes[row, col].set_title(f'多项式回归 (阶数 {degree}), R²={scores[f\"poly_{degree}\"]:.3f}')\n",
    "            axes[row, col].legend()\n",
    "            axes[row, col].grid(True, alpha=0.3)\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # 4.3.2 分段回归结果\n",
    "    if piecewise_score > 0:\n",
    "        axes[2, 0].scatter(x_rating, y_clean, alpha=0.3, s=10)\n",
    "        x_plot = np.linspace(x_rating.min(), x_rating.max(), 100)\n",
    "        y_plot = piecewise_linear(x_plot, a, b, c, d, breakpoint)\n",
    "        axes[2, 0].plot(x_plot, y_plot, 'g-', linewidth=2, label='分段线性')\n",
    "        axes[2, 0].axvline(x=breakpoint, color='red', linestyle='--', alpha=0.7, label='转折点')\n",
    "        axes[2, 0].set_xlabel('评分')\n",
    "        axes[2, 0].set_ylabel('Log(下载量)')\n",
    "        axes[2, 0].set_title(f'分段线性回归, R²={piecewise_score:.3f}')\n",
    "        axes[2, 0].legend()\n",
    "        axes[2, 0].grid(True, alpha=0.3)\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # 4.3.3 模型性能比较\n",
    "    model_names = list(scores.keys())\n",
    "    model_scores = list(scores.values())\n",
    "    if piecewise_score > 0:\n",
    "        model_names.append('piecewise')\n",
    "        model_scores.append(piecewise_score)\n",
    "    \n",
    "    bars = axes[2, 1].bar(range(len(model_names)), model_scores, color='skyblue', alpha=0.7)\n",
    "    axes[2, 1].set_xticks(range(len(model_names)))\n",
    "    axes[2, 1].set_xticklabels(model_names, rotation=45)\n",
    "    axes[2, 1].set_ylabel('R² 得分')\n",
    "    axes[2, 1].set_title('模型性能比较')\n",
    "    axes[2, 1].grid(True, alpha=0.3)\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # 在柱状图上显示数值\n",
    "    for bar, score in zip(bars, model_scores):\n",
    "        height = bar.get_height()\n",
    "        axes[2, 1].text(bar.get_x() + bar.get_width()/2., height,\n",
    "                       f'{score:.3f}', ha='center', va='bottom')\n",
    "    \n",
    "    plt.tight_layout()\n",
    "    plt.show()\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # 4.4 额外分析：价格效应可视化\n",
    "    fig, axes = plt.subplots(1, 2, figsize=(14, 6))\n",
    "    fig.suptitle('价格和评分对下载量的影响', fontsize=14, fontweight='bold')\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # 价格 vs 下载量\n",
    "    axes[0].scatter(X_clean['Price_Clean'], y_clean, alpha=0.5, s=20)\n",
    "    axes[0].set_xlabel('价格')\n",
    "    axes[0].set_ylabel('Log(下载量)')\n",
    "    axes[0].set_title('价格 vs 下载量')\n",
    "    axes[0].grid(True, alpha=0.3)\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # 创建价格区间分析\n",
    "    price_bins = pd.cut(X_clean['Price_Clean'], bins=5, labels=['很低', '低', '中', '高', '很高'])\n",
    "    price_download_stats = pd.DataFrame({\n",
    "        'price_range': price_bins,\n",
    "        'log_downloads': y_clean\n",
    "    }).groupby('price_range')['log_downloads'].agg(['mean', 'std', 'count']).reset_index()\n",
    "    \n",
    "    axes[1].bar(range(len(price_download_stats)), price_download_stats['mean'], \n",
    "               yerr=price_download_stats['std'], alpha=0.7, color='lightcoral')\n",
    "    axes[1].set_xticks(range(len(price_download_stats)))\n",
    "    axes[1].set_xticklabels(price_download_stats['price_range'], rotation=45)\n",
    "    axes[1].set_ylabel('平均 Log(下载量)')\n",
    "    axes[1].set_title('不同价格区间的平均下载量')\n",
    "    axes[1].grid(True, alpha=0.3)\n",
    "    \n",
    "    plt.tight_layout()\n",
    "    plt.show()\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # 4.5 总结建模结果\n",
    "    print(f\"\\n建模结果总结:\")\n",
    "    best_model_name = max(scores.keys(), key=lambda k: scores[k])\n",
    "    print(f\"最佳模型: {best_model_name} (R² = {scores[best_model_name]:.4f})\")\n",
    "    \n",
    "    if piecewise_score > 0:\n",
    "        print(f\"分段回归 R² = {piecewise_score:.4f}\")\n",
    "        if piecewise_score > scores[best_model_name]:\n",
    "            print(\"分段回归表现最佳，表明评分对下载量有明显的非线性转折点\")\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # 特征重要性分析（基于最佳多项式模型）\n",
    "    if hasattr(models[best_model_name].named_steps['regressor'], 'coef_'):\n",
    "        coefficients = models[best_model_name].named_steps['regressor'].coef_\n",
    "        feature_names = models[best_model_name].named_steps['poly'].get_feature_names_out(['Rating', 'Price_Clean'])\n",
    "        \n",
    "        print(f\"\\n特征重要性 (基于 {best_model_name}):\")\n",
    "        feature_importance = list(zip(feature_names, coefficients))\n",
    "        feature_importance.sort(key=lambda x: abs(x[1]), reverse=True)\n",
    "        \n",
    "        for name, coef in feature_importance:\n",
    "            if abs(coef) > 0.001:  # 只显示重要特征\n",
    "                print(f\"  {name}: {coef:.4f}\")\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # 4.6 商业解释\n",
    "    print(f\"\\n商业洞察:\")\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # 计算相关系数\n",
    "    rating_corr = np.corrcoef(X_clean['Rating'], y_clean)[0, 1]\n",
    "    price_corr = np.corrcoef(X_clean['Price_Clean'], y_clean)[0, 1]\n",
    "    \n",
    "    print(f\"评分与下载量相关性: {rating_corr:.3f}\")\n",
    "    print(f\"价格与下载量相关性: {price_corr:.3f}\")\n",
    "    \n",
    "    if rating_corr > 0.1:\n",
    "        print(\"- 评分对下载量有正向影响，提高应用质量和用户满意度很重要\")\n",
    "    if price_corr < -0.1:\n",
    "        print(\"- 价格对下载量有负向影响，定价策略需要谨慎考虑\")\n",
    "    elif abs(price_corr) < 0.1:\n",
    "        print(\"- 价格对下载量影响较小，可能存在其他更重要的因素\")\n",
    "    \n",
    "    if piecewise_score > 0 and breakpoint > 0:\n",
    "        print(f\"- 评分存在转折点({breakpoint:.2f})，可能表明用户对应用质量有最低期望\")\n",
    "    \n",
    "    return models, scores\n",
    "\n",
    "# 主函数：运行所有分析\n",
    "def run_advanced_analysis(df):\n",

    "def advanced_modeling(df):\n",
    "    \"\"\"\n",
    "    高级机器学习建模分析：预测应用下载量\n",
    "    使用多种特征工程和机器学习算法\n",
    "    \"\"\"\n",
    "    print(\"\\n=== 高级机器学习建模分析 ===\")\n",
    "    print(\"目标变量：下载量 (Log transformed)\")\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # 1. 特征工程\n",
    "    print(\"\\n1. 特征工程...\")\n",
    "    df_model = df.copy()\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # 1.1 基础特征处理\n",
    "    df_model['Log_Installs'] = np.log10(df_model['Installs_Clean'] + 1)\n",
    "    df_model['Rating_filled'] = df_model['Rating'].fillna(df_model['Rating'].mean())\n",
    "    df_model['Price_filled'] = df_model['Price_Clean'].fillna(0)\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # 1.2 创建新特征\n",
    "    # 评分相关特征\n",
    "    df_model['Rating_squared'] = df_model['Rating_filled'] ** 2\n",
    "    df_model['Rating_cubed'] = df_model['Rating_filled'] ** 3\n",
    "    df_model['High_Rating'] = (df_model['Rating_filled'] >= 4.5).astype(int)\n",
    "    df_model['Low_Rating'] = (df_model['Rating_filled'] <= 3.0).astype(int)\n",
    "    df_model['Rating_deviation'] = np.abs(df_model['Rating_filled'] - df_model['Rating_filled'].mean())\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # 价格相关特征\n",
    "    df_model['Is_Free'] = (df_model['Price_filled'] == 0).astype(int)\n",
    "    df_model['Is_Premium'] = (df_model['Price_filled'] > 5).astype(int)\n",
    "    df_model['Price_log'] = np.log10(df_model['Price_filled'] + 1)\n",
    "    df_model['Price_tier'] = pd.cut(df_model['Price_filled'], \n",
    "                                   bins=[-0.1, 0, 1, 5, 20, 100], \n",
    "                                   labels=['Free', 'Low', 'Mid', 'High', 'Premium'])\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # 分类相关特征\n",
    "    if 'Category' in df_model.columns:\n",
    "        category_encoder = LabelEncoder()\n",
    "        df_model['Category_encoded'] = category_encoder.fit_transform(df_model['Category'].fillna('Unknown'))\n",
    "        \n",
    "        # 分类流行度\n",
    "        category_popularity = df_model.groupby('Category')['Log_Installs'].mean()\n",
    "        df_model['Category_popularity'] = df_model['Category'].map(category_popularity).fillna(category_popularity.mean())\n",
    "    \n",
    "\n",
    "    # 文本特征（如果有应用名称）\n",
    "    if 'App Name' in df_model.columns:\n",
    "        df_model['App_name_length'] = df_model['App Name'].str.len()\n",
    "        df_model['App_name_words'] = df_model['App Name'].str.split().str.len()\n",
    "        df_model['Has_numbers'] = df_model['App Name'].str.contains(r'\\d').astype(int)\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # 交互特征\n",
    "    df_model['Rating_Price_interaction'] = df_model['Rating_filled'] * df_model['Price_filled']\n",
    "    df_model['Rating_Free_interaction'] = df_model['Rating_filled'] * df_model['Is_Free']\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # 1.3 选择建模特征\n",
    "    feature_columns = [\n",
    "        'Rating_filled', 'Rating_squared', 'Rating_cubed', 'High_Rating', 'Low_Rating', 'Rating_deviation',\n",
    "        'Price_filled', 'Price_log', 'Is_Free', 'Is_Premium',\n",
    "        'Rating_Price_interaction', 'Rating_Free_interaction'\n",
    "    ]\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # 添加编码特征\n",
    "    if 'Category_encoded' in df_model.columns:\n",
    "        feature_columns.extend(['Category_encoded', 'Category_popularity'])\n",
    "    if 'App_name_length' in df_model.columns:\n",
    "        feature_columns.extend(['App_name_length', 'App_name_words', 'Has_numbers'])\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # 准备数据\n",
    "    X = df_model[feature_columns].fillna(0)\n",
    "    y = df_model['Log_Installs']\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # 移除异常值\n",
    "    mask = (np.abs(stats.zscore(X.select_dtypes(include=[np.number]))) < 3).all(axis=1) & \\\n",
    "           (np.abs(stats.zscore(y)) < 3)\n",
    "    X_clean = X[mask]\n",
    "    y_clean = y[mask]\n",
    "    \n",
    "    print(f\"特征数量: {X_clean.shape[1]}\")\n",
    "    print(f\"样本数量: {X_clean.shape[0]}\")\n",
    "    print(f\"特征列表: {list(X_clean.columns)}\")\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # 2. 数据分割\n",
    "    X_train, X_test, y_train, y_test = train_test_split(\n",
    "        X_clean, y_clean, test_size=0.2, random_state=42\n",
    "    )\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # 3. 模型定义和训练\n",
    "    print(\"\\n2. 模型训练和评估...\")\n",
    "    \n",
    "    models = {\n",
    "        'Linear Regression': LinearRegression(),\n",
    "        'Ridge': Ridge(alpha=1.0),\n",
    "        'Lasso': Lasso(alpha=0.1),\n",
    "        'ElasticNet': ElasticNet(alpha=0.1, l1_ratio=0.5),\n",
    "        'Random Forest': RandomForestRegressor(n_estimators=100, random_state=42),\n",
    "        'Gradient Boosting': GradientBoostingRegressor(n_estimators=100, random_state=42),\n",
    "        'SVR': SVR(kernel='rbf', C=100, gamma='scale'),\n",
    "        'Neural Network': MLPRegressor(hidden_layer_sizes=(100, 50), max_iter=1000, random_state=42),\n",
    "        'Decision Tree': DecisionTreeRegressor(random_state=42)\n",
    "    }\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # 存储结果\n",
    "    results = {}\n",
    "    predictions = {}\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # 标准化特征\n",
    "    scaler = StandardScaler()\n",
    "    X_train_scaled = scaler.fit_transform(X_train)\n",
    "    X_test_scaled = scaler.transform(X_test)\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # 训练和评估模型\n",
    "    for name, model in models.items():\n",
    "        print(f\"训练 {name}...\")\n",
    "        \n",
    "        # 对需要标准化的模型使用标准化数据\n",
    "        if name in ['SVR', 'Neural Network', 'Ridge', 'Lasso', 'ElasticNet']:\n",
    "            model.fit(X_train_scaled, y_train)\n",
    "            y_pred = model.predict(X_test_scaled)\n",
    "            \n",
    "            # 交叉验证\n",
    "            cv_scores = cross_val_score(model, X_train_scaled, y_train, cv=5, scoring='r2')\n",
    "        else:\n",
    "            model.fit(X_train, y_train)\n",
    "            y_pred = model.predict(X_test)\n",
    "            \n",
    "            # 交叉验证\n",
    "            cv_scores = cross_val_score(model, X_train, y_train, cv=5, scoring='r2')\n",
    "        \n",
    "        # 计算评估指标\n",

    "# ===============================\n",
    "# 5.1 统计检验\n",
    "# ===============================\n",
    "\n",
    "import numpy as np\n",
    "from scipy import stats\n",
    "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n",
    "import seaborn as sns\n",
    "\n",
    "def comprehensive_statistical_testing(free_ratings, paid_ratings):\n",
    "    \"\"\"\n",
    "    对两组数据进行全面的统计检验\n",
    "    \"\"\"\n",
    "    print(\"=== 数据描述性统计 ===\")\n",
    "    print(f\"免费应用: n={len(free_ratings)}, 均值={free_ratings.mean():.3f}, 标准差={free_ratings.std():.3f}\")\n",
    "    print(f\"付费应用: n={len(paid_ratings)}, 均值={paid_ratings.mean():.3f}, 标准差={paid_ratings.std():.3f}\")\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # 1. 正态性检验\n",
    "    print(\"\\n=== 正态性检验 ===\")\n",
    "    _, free_shapiro_p = stats.shapiro(free_ratings.sample(5000) if len(free_ratings) > 5000 else free_ratings)\n",
    "    _, paid_shapiro_p = stats.shapiro(paid_ratings.sample(5000) if len(paid_ratings) > 5000 else paid_ratings)\n",
    "    print(f\"免费应用 Shapiro-Wilk检验 p值: {free_shapiro_p:.6f}\")\n",
    "    print(f\"付费应用 Shapiro-Wilk检验 p值: {paid_shapiro_p:.6f}\")\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # 2. 方差齐性检验\n",
    "    print(\"\\n=== 方差齐性检验 ===\")\n",
    "    _, levene_p = stats.levene(free_ratings, paid_ratings)\n",
    "    print(f\"Levene检验 p值: {levene_p:.6f}\")\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # 3. 选择合适的检验方法\n",
    "    print(\"\\n=== 均值差异检验 ===\")\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # 3.1 标准t检验（假设等方差）\n",
    "    t_stat, t_p = stats.ttest_ind(free_ratings, paid_ratings, equal_var=True)\n",
    "    print(f\"标准t检验: t={t_stat:.4f}, p={t_p:.6f}\")\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # 3.2 Welch t检验（不假设等方差）\n",
    "    welch_t, welch_p = stats.ttest_ind(free_ratings, paid_ratings, equal_var=False)\n",
    "    print(f\"Welch t检验: t={welch_t:.4f}, p={welch_p:.6f}\")\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # 3.3 Mann-Whitney U检验（非参数）\n",
    "    u_stat, u_p = stats.mannwhitneyu(free_ratings, paid_ratings, alternative='two-sided')\n",
    "    print(f\"Mann-Whitney U检验: U={u_stat:.4f}, p={u_p:.6f}\")\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # 3.4 Kolmogorov-Smirnov检验\n",
    "    ks_stat, ks_p = stats.ks_2samp(free_ratings, paid_ratings)\n",
    "    print(f\"K-S检验: D={ks_stat:.4f}, p={ks_p:.6f}\")\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # 4. 效应大小计算\n",
    "    print(\"\\n=== 效应大小 ===\")\n",
    "    # Cohen's d\n",
    "    pooled_std = np.sqrt(((len(free_ratings)-1)*free_ratings.var() + \n",
    "                         (len(paid_ratings)-1)*paid_ratings.var()) / \n",
    "                        (len(free_ratings) + len(paid_ratings) - 2))\n",
    "    cohens_d = (paid_ratings.mean() - free_ratings.mean()) / pooled_std\n",
    "    print(f\"Cohen's d: {cohens_d:.4f}\")\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # 5. 推荐检验方法\n",
    "    print(\"\\n=== 检验方法推荐 ===\")\n",
    "    normal_free = free_shapiro_p > 0.05\n",
    "    normal_paid = paid_shapiro_p > 0.05\n",
    "    equal_var = levene_p > 0.05\n",
    "    \n",
    "    if normal_free and normal_paid:\n",
    "        if equal_var:\n",
    "            print(\"推荐: 标准t检验（数据正态分布且方差齐性）\")\n",
    "            recommended_p = t_p\n",
    "        else:\n",
    "            print(\"推荐: Welch t检验（数据正态分布但方差不齐）\")\n",
    "            recommended_p = welch_p\n",
    "    else:\n",
    "        print(\"推荐: Mann-Whitney U检验（数据非正态分布）\")\n",
    "        recommended_p = u_p\n",
    "    \n",
    "    print(f\"推荐检验的p值: {recommended_p:.6f}\")\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # 6. 结果解释\n",
    "    print(\"\\n=== 结果解释 ===\")\n",
    "    alpha = 0.05\n",
    "    if recommended_p < alpha:\n",
    "        print(f\"结论: 在α={alpha}显著性水平下，拒绝原假设\")\n",
    "        print(\"付费应用与免费应用的评分存在显著差异\")\n",
    "    else:\n",
    "        print(f\"结论: 在α={alpha}显著性水平下，不能拒绝原假设\")\n",
    "        print(\"付费应用与免费应用的评分无显著差异\")\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # 效应大小解释\n",
    "    if abs(cohens_d) < 0.2:\n",
    "        effect_size = \"小\"\n",
    "    elif abs(cohens_d) < 0.5:\n",
    "        effect_size = \"中等\"\n",
    "    elif abs(cohens_d) < 0.8:\n",
    "        effect_size = \"大\"\n",
    "    else:\n",
    "        effect_size = \"非常大\"\n",
    "    \n",
    "    print(f\"效应大小: {effect_size} (Cohen's d = {cohens_d:.3f})\")\n",
    "\n",
    "def bootstrap_confidence_interval(data1, data2, n_bootstrap=10000, confidence=0.95):\n",
    "    \"\"\"\n",
    "    使用Bootstrap方法计算均值差异的置信区间\n",
    "    \"\"\"\n",
    "    bootstrap_diffs = []\n",
    "    \n",
    "    for _ in range(n_bootstrap):\n",
    "        sample1 = np.random.choice(data1, size=len(data1), replace=True)\n",
    "        sample2 = np.random.choice(data2, size=len(data2), replace=True)\n",
    "        bootstrap_diffs.append(np.mean(sample2) - np.mean(sample1))\n",
    "    \n",
    "    alpha = 1 - confidence\n",
    "    lower = np.percentile(bootstrap_diffs, 100 * alpha/2)\n",
    "    upper = np.percentile(bootstrap_diffs, 100 * (1 - alpha/2))\n",
    "    \n",
    "    print(f\"\\n=== Bootstrap {confidence*100}%置信区间 ===\")\n",
    "    print(f\"均值差异的{confidence*100}%置信区间: [{lower:.4f}, {upper:.4f}]\")\n",
    "    \n",
    "    return lower, upper\n",
    "\n",
    "# 使用示例：\n",
    "comprehensive_statistical_testing(free_ratings, paid_ratings)\n",
    "bootstrap_confidence_interval(free_ratings, paid_ratings)"
   ]
  },

    "# ===============================\n",
    "# 5.2 统计检验\n",
    "# ===============================\n",
    "\n",
    "print(\"\\n=== 统计显著性检验 ===\")\n",
    "\n",
    "# T检验：免费vs付费应用的评分差异\n",
    "free_ratings = df_analysis[df_analysis['Price_Clean'] == 0]['Rating']\n",
    "paid_ratings = df_analysis[df_analysis['Price_Clean'] > 0]['Rating']\n",
    "\n",
    "t_stat, t_p_value = stats.ttest_ind(free_ratings, paid_ratings)\n",
    "print(f\"免费 vs 付费应用评分 t检验:\")\n",
    "print(f\"t统计量: {t_stat:.4f}, p值: {t_p_value:.4f}\")\n",
    "\n",
    "# Mann-Whitney U检验（非参数检验）\n",
    "u_stat, u_p_value = stats.mannwhitneyu(free_ratings, paid_ratings, alternative='two-sided')\n",
    "print(f\"Mann-Whitney U检验:\")\n",
    "print(f\"U统计量: {u_stat:.4f}, p值: {u_p_value:.4f}\")\n",
    "\n",
    "# ===============================\n",
    "# 6. NLP分析 - 应用名称特征提取\n",
    "# ===============================\n",
    "\n",
    "print(\"\\n=== NLP特征提取 - 基于应用名称分析 ===\")\n",
    "\n",
    "# 下载NLTK数据（首次运行需要）\n",
    "try:\n",
    "    nltk.data.find('tokenizers/punkt')\n",
    "    nltk.data.find('corpora/stopwords')\n",
    "    nltk.data.find('corpora/wordnet')\n",
    "except LookupError:\n",
    "    nltk.download('punkt')\n",
    "    nltk.download('stopwords')\n",
    "    nltk.download('wordnet')\n",
    "\n",
    "# 文本预处理函数\n",
    "def preprocess_text(text):\n",
    "    if pd.isna(text):\n",
    "        return \"\"\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # 转小写\n",
    "    text = text.lower()\n",
    "    # 移除特殊字符和数字\n",
    "    text = re.sub(r'[^a-zA-Z\\s]', '', text)\n",
    "    # 分词\n",
    "    tokens = word_tokenize(text)\n",
    "    # 移除停用词\n",
    "    stop_words = set(stopwords.words('english'))\n",
    "    tokens = [token for token in tokens if token not in stop_words and len(token) > 2]\n",
    "    # 词形还原\n",
    "    lemmatizer = WordNetLemmatizer()\n",
    "    tokens = [lemmatizer.lemmatize(token) for token in tokens]\n",
    "    \n",
    "    return ' '.join(tokens)\n",
    "\n",
    "# 预处理应用名称\n",
    "df_analysis['App_Name_Clean'] = df_analysis['App Name'].apply(preprocess_text)\n",
    "\n",
    "# 移除空应用名称\n",
    "df_nlp = df_analysis[df_analysis['App_Name_Clean'].str.len() > 0].copy()\n",
    "\n",
    "if len(df_nlp) > 0:\n",
    "    # N-gram特征提取\n",
    "    # Bi-gram分析\n",
    "    bigram_vectorizer = CountVectorizer(ngram_range=(2, 2), max_features=100, min_df=10)\n",
    "    bigram_matrix = bigram_vectorizer.fit_transform(df_nlp['App_Name_Clean'])\n",
    "    bigram_features = bigram_vectorizer.get_feature_names_out()\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # Tri-gram分析  \n",
    "    trigram_vectorizer = CountVectorizer(ngram_range=(3, 3), max_features=50, min_df=5)\n",
    "    trigram_matrix = trigram_vectorizer.fit_transform(df_nlp['App_Name_Clean'])\n",
    "    trigram_features = trigram_vectorizer.get_feature_names_out()\n",
    "    \n",
    "    print(\"最常见的Bi-grams (应用名称):\")\n",
    "    bigram_counts = np.sum(bigram_matrix.toarray(), axis=0)\n",
    "    bigram_freq = list(zip(bigram_features, bigram_counts))\n",
    "    bigram_freq.sort(key=lambda x: x[1], reverse=True)\n",
    "    for feature, count in bigram_freq[:10]:\n",
    "        print(f\"'{feature}': {count}\")\n",
    "    \n",
    "    print(\"\\n最常见的Tri-grams (应用名称):\")\n",
    "    trigram_counts = np.sum(trigram_matrix.toarray(), axis=0)\n",
    "    trigram_freq = list(zip(trigram_features, trigram_counts))\n",
    "    trigram_freq.sort(key=lambda x: x[1], reverse=True)\n",
    "    for feature, count in trigram_freq[:10]:\n",
    "        print(f\"'{feature}': {count}\")\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # 聚类分析\n",
    "    tfidf_vectorizer = TfidfVectorizer(max_features=200, min_df=10, max_df=0.8)\n",
    "    tfidf_matrix = tfidf_vectorizer.fit_transform(df_nlp['App_Name_Clean'])\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # K-means聚类\n",
    "    n_clusters = 8\n",
    "    kmeans = KMeans(n_clusters=n_clusters, random_state=42, n_init=10)\n",
    "    clusters = kmeans.fit_predict(tfidf_matrix)\n",
    "    \n",
    "    df_nlp['Cluster'] = clusters\n",
    "    \n",
    "    print(f\"\\n应用聚类结果 (基于应用名称, K={n_clusters}):\")\n",
    "    for i in range(n_clusters):\n",
    "        cluster_apps = df_nlp[df_nlp['Cluster'] == i]\n",
    "        if len(cluster_apps) > 0:\n",
    "            print(f\"聚类 {i}: {len(cluster_apps)} 个应用\")\n",
    "            print(f\"平均评分: {cluster_apps['Rating'].mean():.2f}\")\n",
    "            print(f\"平均价格: ${cluster_apps['Price_Clean'].mean():.2f}\")\n",
    "            print(f\"平均安装量: {cluster_apps['Installs_Clean'].mean():.0f}\")\n",
    "            # 显示聚类中最常见的词汇\n",
    "            cluster_center = kmeans.cluster_centers_[i]\n",
    "            top_features_idx = cluster_center.argsort()[-5:][::-1]\n",
    "            feature_names = tfidf_vectorizer.get_feature_names_out()\n",
    "            top_features = [feature_names[idx] for idx in top_features_idx]\n",
    "            print(f\"关键词: {', '.join(top_features)}\")\n",
    "            print()\n",
    "\n",
    "    # 分析不同聚类的表现\n",
    "    cluster_performance = df_nlp.groupby('Cluster').agg({\n",
    "        'Rating': ['mean', 'std'],\n",
    "        'Price_Clean': ['mean', 'median'],\n",
    "        'Installs_Clean': ['mean', 'median'],\n",
    "        'App Name': 'count'\n",
    "    }).round(3)\n",
    "    \n",
    "    print(\"各聚类表现对比:\")\n",
    "    print(cluster_performance)\n"
   ]
  },
